1428
01:34:13,356 --> 01:34:17,193
<i>Twisted faces in the clouds</i>

1429
01:34:23,783 --> 01:34:27,787
<i>Let unanswered question marks
Fall where they will</i>

1430
01:34:30,373 --> 01:34:34,585
<i>The thoughts that imprison me
Walk with me still</i>

1431
01:34:37,088 --> 01:34:41,091
<i>And seconds that fly by
Like days of my life</i>

1432
01:34:41,092 --> 01:34:46,180
<i>Were hours spent wasted
On chasing the words of the wise</i>

